        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks WAL for specimens and observations [on scarlet runner beans]. CD is perplexed whether to account for the changes as due to simple variation or to crossing. The information will be used when he finally comes to a conclusion on the subject [see <hi rend="italic">Cross and self-fertilisation</hi>, p. 151].</p> 
        </abstract>
